Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.13,0:00:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神代瑪雅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔界的大門勢必會打開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有礙事的人統統受死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.50,0:00:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你的父親那樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你殺了爸爸？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.41,0:00:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能過去…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是殺死爸爸的仇人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.46,0:00:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.91,0:00:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐就請逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們就由千尋我來擋住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.35,0:00:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我去死吧！白魔法師！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}借千之風 尋找美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲～ 要穿進去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:02:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炎！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:02:57.72,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(936,974)}Ignis
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.92,0:03:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逗你玩的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我放下 我也要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我放下 把我放下來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.31,0:03:33.35,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}殺魔女 毀魔窟…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.65,0:03:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猛禽獸！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:51.86,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(928,974)}Avis Rapax
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.99,0:04:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然把魔物連續召喚過來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯的仿造品對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人不也很歡樂的樣子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連小命被盯上了也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許愚弄大小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅沒降臨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼反應都沒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅或許就在附近也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通靈板與通靈術都不行的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就只剩這個了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探測棒怎麼可能把靈召喚出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有反應了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,院子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慘烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼火 是鬼火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅一定就在那裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺魔女 毀魔窟…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不是鬼火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙是要幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降靈成功了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老娘還好好活著呢 趕緊逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:48.25,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}殺魔女 殺魔女 殺魔女…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅她…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.43,0:06:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不賴嘛 白魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就看看 你的氣勢能撐多久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 那位大人很強大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃到城外去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑魔女的目標是你 請稍事忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是為了我們的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你去到大小姐那邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 好可怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是用這種淫蕩的聲音去魅惑那個人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美風小姐 我一直被你騙了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 要對他下手簡直不費吹灰之力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這鎮上的人們也是呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺魔女 毀魔窟…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦賣噶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梢！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又咋了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 梢消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.70,0:07:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就知道那女孩總有一天會妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在校外把她幹掉倒是不易
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是那個男人出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託他以後馬上就放我進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾開！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 後面！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是神馬東西啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 這邊也有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對他用了什麼卑鄙手段？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是給他溫柔地撓了撓癢癢罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.55,0:08:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加報酬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要一年份的布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 拜託你們兩個了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.34,0:08:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人真是單純
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給點甜頭就搖頭擺尾了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個人的心靈是純淨無瑕的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想的東西多著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是純潔的愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿盈的全是慾望啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人都是只想滿足自己慾望的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會用愛填滿一切！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是你的幻覺而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛可以構建起幸福的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Smile！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊也忙著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛什麼的說到底還不是為了肉體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛是發自內心的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就當一輩子愛的魔法師吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎 我和那個人接吻過了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…副校長她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人逃走什麼的 我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.63,0:10:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅大人你保護好自己的生命 是純一郎大人的夙願
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是爸爸他已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙殺了爸爸 甚至連副校長也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.31,0:10:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後還想毀滅世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能只是默默地看著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能讓那樣的事情發生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 坐上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有打倒黑魔女的辦法嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.37,0:10:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 一個都沒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我砍了你 神代瑪雅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副校長…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.71,0:11:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能幫我轉達給大小姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一郎大人還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.53,0:12:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們用和之前一樣的魔法欺騙了敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 校長…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安倍老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.85,0:12:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的祈願 化作翱翔的白鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽翼啊 請為他指引
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去往那遠離悲傷 沒有痛苦 歡樂縈繞的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去往那守候著幸福的明日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去往那光芒永駐的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑木！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來的正好 帶我去瑪雅那…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好沒 亞美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上來！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺魔女 搗魔窟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:15.94,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}殺魔女 搗魔窟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.09,0:14:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺魔女～！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是梢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梢也真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腐黑咒！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:17.55,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(928,974)}Nigredo
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:17.55,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Nigredo：煉金術用語中指代腐敗或分解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 爸爸的筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為已經燒掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是別的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副校長事先把裡面的內容交換了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這上面寫著封印你的咒語
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.33,0:15:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我們只是在一味亂竄而已嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.77,0:15:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打倒黑魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.64,0:15:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要作為筆記繼承人的你和學院的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了發動咒語 我們要去瓦爾德施泰因學院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被逼上絕路的 其實是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筆記…！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法發動的話就僅僅是堆紙而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個學校就是你的墓碑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過嘛 世界毀滅的話 這裡也會消失就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會…讓你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 都要死的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文明！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 都說了讓你等等的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:42.07,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}瑪雅 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要那麼著急嘛 馬上就能兩人獨處了嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:46.35,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}現在就來救你！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就會享有永遠的快樂…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:49.52,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}瑪雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.46,0:17:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師～我想無視別人是不好的哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心跳不已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 我的身體 是這樣的愉悅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文明！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙就是諾查丹瑪斯之鑰！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.04,0:17:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞毛啊你！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徒勞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:03.33,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(964,974)}Debris magia territory
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破碎魔法領域
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 那個確實是消滅魔鬼的咒語啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是遺憾 由你來誦讀的話就沒效果…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:17.73,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(964,974)}Debris magia territory
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破碎魔法領域
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:23.37,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(968,974)}Leno nenia finis
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安詳歎歌終焉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.88,0:18:27.29,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(968,974)}Leno nenia finis
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.88,0:18:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安詳歎歌終焉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:29.73,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(976,974)}Regina canorus
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王呵 輕吟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:32.46,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(976,974)}Regina canorus
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王呵 輕吟
