Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一曲搖籃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:37.71,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(968,974)}Domina cantlena
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一曲搖籃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:39.19,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(936,974)}Mise…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:50.98,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(964,974)}Miserere area
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相憐之地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.97,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(964,974)}Miserere area
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相憐之地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能！為什麼還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.39,0:18:57.90,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(932,974)}Lucis ortho
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.39,0:18:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬丈流明！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:19:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能 我的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:01.32,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Lucis ortho
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}萬丈流明！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:04.54,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(940,974)}Leo…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下來 停下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:13.35,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(940,974)}Leo ortus en necto
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅心我縛！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點疼…和瑪雅打的比起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.25,0:19:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是太溫柔了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你這變態～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:33.54,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(940,974)}Leo ortus en necto
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅心我縛！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:44.10,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(932,974)}Mille gladius
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千刃向汝！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺魔女…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為 為什麼連你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…消滅一切魔物…的咒語…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於黑暗中誕生之物…便要回歸於黑暗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願您…好運…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.21,0:21:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你知道咒語是哪一頁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.39,0:21:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是副校長…千尋小姐她告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.83,0:21:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我好怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.22,0:21:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是No. 6
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙已經找到 並且已經毀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去外面吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是我們的勝利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:21:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.08,0:23:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 文明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.44,0:23:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.50,0:23:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平的未來會在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.56,0:23:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.11,0:23:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒見過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.90,0:23:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我們會見到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.84,0:23:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要回未來去…了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.40,0:24:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世紀末超自然學院
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.32,0:24:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大結局 瑪雅的文明
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.82,0:24:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因超自然 我們相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
